<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a01"/><p id="pI01p0094a0101">郭世貴一心供養
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a02"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a03"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a04"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a05"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a06"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a07"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a08"/>清信駱花嬰
<lb ed="C I" n="0094a09"/>一心供養佛時</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b01"/><p id="pI01p0094b0101">夫大覺神<note n="0094001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30634;＝遷【史】</note><app n="0094001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30634;</rdg></app>。非經像無以表其
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b02"/>真。益世閏時。<note n="0094002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02712;＝憑【史】</note><app n="0094002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">憑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02712;</rdg></app>形<note n="0094003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01581;＝質【史】</note><app n="0094003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">質</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01581;</rdg></app>如<note n="0094004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30627;＝取【史】</note><app n="0094004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">取</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30627;</rdg></app>利。然
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b03"/>僧<note n="0094005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30633;＝演【史】</note><app n="0094005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">演</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30633;</rdg></app>減割衣&CB00425;之資。造石像壹
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b04"/>區。金像三區。<note n="0094006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30628;＝浮【史】</note><app n="0094006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">浮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30628;</rdg></app><note n="0094007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30629;＝圖【史】</note><app n="0094007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30629;</rdg></app>三級。大般<note n="0094008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30630;＝涅【史】</note><app n="0094008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">涅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30630;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b05"/>槃經<note n="0094009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30631;＝兩【史】</note><app n="0094009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兩</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30631;</rdg></app>部。雜經三百<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">品</unclear>。供養僧
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b06"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">卅</unclear>人。上為　<note n="0094010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18910;＝國【史】</note><app n="0094010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">國</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18910;</rdg></app>主。百僚。師徒<note n="0094011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30632;＝所【史】</note><app n="0094011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30632;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b07"/>生。法界之<note n="0094012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30635;＝類【史】</note><app n="0094012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">類</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30635;</rdg></app>。咸同正覺。
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b08"/>大統四年。<note n="0094013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15329;＝歲【史】</note><app n="0094013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15329;</rdg></app>次<note n="0094014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07436;＝戊【史】</note><app n="0094014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07436;</rdg></app>午。七月十五
<lb ed="C I" n="0094b09"/>日。比丘僧<app source="0094005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">演</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30633;</rdg></app>敬造供養。</p>
</div2>
